Now I understand the pattern. The current function only handles `ICMP_UGT` with `SMIN`. I need to add support for `ICMP_EQ` with the full mask `(SMin | (DivC - 1))`.

When using `ICMP_EQ`, the comparison is `(X & Mask) == Mask` where `Mask = SMin | (DivC - 1)`. This is equivalent to `(X & Mask) >u SMin`.

Let me modify the function to also accept `ICMP_EQ` with the mask being `SMin | (DivC - 1)`.

The modification: currently lines 1241-1245 check for `ICMP_UGT` with `SMIN`. I need to extend this to also check for `ICMP_EQ` with the full mask.

